{"tid":229643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"生痱滋會唔會係最痛苦嘅其中一件事？","createTime":"2017-05-04T17:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T13:49:03.000Z","uid":95908,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52fb6361975766b872bec2dec20209336628d1fa","tid":229643,"uid":95908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"小弟一係唔生 一生就生番3-4粒<br />\n我係果種一個月固定生一次嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排生親都係條脷度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早兩日又生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次又係脷尖<br />\n一大兩細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大果粒係兩粒細痴埋一齊變出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家只要hi到就標曬眼水咁<br />\n食飯係最慘嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明今日嘅餸係我最中意食 都搞到唔想掂佢<br />\n因為個餸係豉油汁底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豉油hi粒痱滋就 真係high出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩方法啊 大家救下我啦"},{"pid":"578b65d77d3348a92855bea365c937e2f2770054","tid":229643,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63b142092701ac3f6b3af17f50ddffc4d4361140","tid":229643,"uid":95908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食奇異果</blockquote><br />\n我好似冇咩用"},{"pid":"e5d334b9f27716abd51880ca7e2db35925589934","tid":229643,"uid":5007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"平時都係留意飲食 我都好易有"},{"pid":"187d6ddbb46e57d79e1dbfe6631dcd36b2cfeab5","tid":229643,"uid":24239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"買支口健樂啦"},{"pid":"79d292087c68fc39139fe9f9b25a3c92a3def5e8","tid":229643,"uid":35403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":