唔知身體出咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc44754c1ebd599f04832db46e56ef62570a80f1","tid":229643,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"生緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2da83aec4f3b72151a44a1398612ad3c8ae7eb","tid":229643,"uid":36722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:39:54.000Z","msg":"我條利 口腔兩邊 上下唇都出哂<br />\n不過係兩三個月一次<br />\n直頭成日都無食野 牙都唔想刷全日訓係床到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fa277effceabbe30d4f5ac5d3a09e905f70a8e","tid":229643,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喉嚨痛先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喉嚨痛食野無痱滋禁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你試過最嚴重嘅喉嚨痛未？<br />\n照落去成個喉嚨都係痱滋，廿幾三十粒<br />\n嗰好講食野喇，水都飲唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果d 係pharyngitis 啦已經 要睇醫生 食藥"},{"pid":"657ea6d4fe410ffd3ceaba8a0c1ca86c03a99ddc","tid":229643,"uid":36722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我條利 口腔兩邊 上下唇都出哂<br />\n不過係兩三個月一次<br />\n直頭成日都無食野 牙都唔想刷全日訓係床到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n補充少少 我就睇中醫無乜用 用好多人介紹既口健樂西瓜霜都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次西醫食類固醇唉"},{"pid":"8ea70ebb5a321a216c9e38f36e90a50991e61e3e","tid":229643,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>偏方<br />\n買樽康鈣c 整碎做幾細塊 然後直接擺係痱滋表面 那完開頭果分鐘就開始唔痛 擺到佢溶曬為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有聽講過</blockquote><br />\n親身試過ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始會唔會好痛？</blockquote><br />\n會<br />\n長痛不如短痛<br />\n你想痛一分鐘定一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好困擾</blockquote><br />\n唔好刺激佢 等佢自己好"},{"pid":"9b7631e51cfa51f58c0a2838fa9c5e1fff678718","tid":229643,"uid":85910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:42:30.000Z","msg":"試過手足口病 喉嚨吞野痛到痴孖根<br />\n好似有個傷口係喉嚨再灑鹽咁痛<br />\n用電筒一照 成個咽喉都係飛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣醫生叫我食雪糕止痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73afa1def0f447a02d5d7cf1afd28af439cf1018","tid":229643,"uid":95908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲多啲水啦</blockquote><br />\n飲水都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1713bef5a761211ba89e96098184fbb37160385","tid":229643,"uid":95908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我依期都生左粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我生左幾日啦"},{"pid":"d3917872b6abe885558293cfae63598a701a9f9d","tid":229643,"uid":95908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食維他命b雜<br />\n<br />\n冇生過 <br />\n<br />\n本身唔小心咬親  心諗大獲<br />\n<br />\n點知冇事  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己咬親 我一定生<br />\n一咬親 我就知仆街啦<br />\n呢幾日無啦"}]}